TENNIS - THAILAND TAKE 2 - 0 LEAD IN DAVIS CUP TIE . HONG KONG , Feb 14 , Reuter - Thailand took a 2 - 0 lead over Hong Kong after the opening singles in their Davis Cup tennis Asia / Oceania Zone Group II first round tie on Friday . Results ( Thailand names first ) : Vorapol Thongkhamchoo beat Mark Ferreira 6 - 3 6 - 2 6 - 0Vittaya Samrej beat Melvin Tong 6 - 3 5 - 7 6 - 2 2 - 6 6 - 4 . 
